  "text": "The pre-processing procedure of the signal consists of three main steps: filtering, de-trending and smoothing. First, a Butterworth bandpass filter with a frequency range of 0.05-100 Hz was used to remove the noise from the ECG signal [CITATION_1] . The resulting signal shows a trended pattern as a result of filtering near the DC component. Therefore, Algorithm 1 was used to stabilize the signal.",
